ssh -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no deploy@prf-project-nodejs-test -p 22 ' rm -rf /app/mobil-webshop-server
cd /app git clone https://github.com/Dobilevi/mobil-webshop-server.git cd /app/mobil-webshop-server git checkout main
npm install npm run build pm2 -f start /app/ecosystem.config.js '

yes | cp -rf /app/environment.ts /app/mobil-webshop-client/src/environments/environment.ts yes | cp -rf /app/environment.ts /app/mobil-webshop-client/src/environments/environment.development.ts
